nt":1},{"word":"favor","count":1},{"word":"egla","count":1},{"word":"town","count":1},{"word":"yellow","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"leave","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Ah, {PlayerName} and Lady Phoebe! I've been capturing the Carnevale's many beautiful moments! What brings you all together here?","quest_name":"What Yesterday Wept, Today Doth Sing","quest_id":114000029},{"text":"Hmm? You took this picture? Look at that composition and lighting! Who knew you had a knack for photography!","quest_name":"What Yesterday Wept, Today Doth Sing","quest_id":114000029},{"text":"Buddy, you look so happy! Whatever the reason, thanks for making this moment special!","quest_name":"What Yesterday Wept, Today Doth Sing","quest_id":114000029},{"text":"{Male=Mr.;Female=Ms.} {PlayerName}, are you in Plushie Village?","quest_name":"Restore Plushie Village II","quest_id":133900006},{"text":"Oh, you've got sharp eyes. It's called Old Bake, an Echo for the apprentices in a bakery.","quest_name":"Restore Plushie Village II","quest_id":133900006},{"text":"Hmm, that may be difficult.","quest_name":"Restore Plushie Village II","quest_id":133900006},{"text":"The villagers said Old Bake's been making bread for almost 60 years. It was only after the old baker passed that it was turned into a teaching oven.","quest_name":"Restore Plushie Village II","quest_id":133900006},{"text":"But there's an issue with its valve—it can't control the fire properly. Seems like the apprentices didn't use it with care.","quest_name":"Restore Plushie Village II","quest_id":133900006},{"text":"It was a lonely stray Echo when we first met. Figured it would be safer for him to stay in the village.","quest_name":"Restore Plushie Village II","quest_id":133900006},{"text":"{Male=Mr.;Female=Ms.} {PlayerName}, could you do me a favor and go to Egla Town <color=yellow>during the day</color> and find out why Old Bake would leave the bakery in the first place?","quest_name":"Restore Plushie Village II","quest_id":133900006}]}